    "Xu et al. (2020) discusses an advanced example of Automatic Speech Recognition (ASR), particularly in the context of noisy environments where traditional ASR systems struggle.",
    "The key example is the Audio-Enhanced Multi-Modality Speech Recognition (AE-MSR) model described in the paper.",
    "(c) Understanding and interpreting multimedia content is enhanced by the integration of visual and auditory information, such as speech or sound, in a process known as \"Vision and Sound.\"",
    "Video analysis utilizes both visual and audio signals to comprehend the scenario, whereas audio-visual speech recognition employs lip movements to improve speech recognition accuracy.",
    "A relevant example of \"Audio-Visual Speech Recognition\" (AVSR) multimodal learning is the Multimodal Sparse Transformer Network (MMST) designed for AVSR."
